data.name: developer.Text
data.value: This software was developed by ODUGBOYE ISRAEL OLUWAGBENGA. ITONE MEDIA PLAYER is an advance multimedia player, with multi-purpose functionality, embedded with the music player functionality and also with the video player functionality. It is engulfed with settings were transparency can be manipulated. Inbuilt voice recognition is attached to this file package, play your music by interacting with your computer system.
